templateAssets.content: The language requirement is automatically fulfilled through coursework completed in preparation for the major.
Due to high demand, admission to SDSU is highly competitive. General admission information is available at:http://arweb.sdsu.edu/es/admissions/transfers/index.html
Complete with a grade of C (2.0) or better: ACCTG 201 and ACCTG 202; ECON 101 and ECON 102; ECON 201 or STAT 119; FIN 240; and MIS 180. These courses cannot be taken for credit/no credit (Cr/NC);
